<H1 ALIGN=Center><B>Amazon Nation Alliance</B></H1><br>
<br>
<P ALIGN=Center><br>
<I><B>In a time when it was believed that the Amazon Nations had died.  There were  those who still believed in their kind.  These proud women continued to grow stronger in their belief of who they are and their athelfi (sisters).  They never forgot why they became an amazon or why their blood ancestors chose this path for them.  They were amazons, women who ruled their own hearts and stood beside their tribal members no matter what the cost.  </B></I></P><br>
<br>
<P ALIGN=Center><br>
<I><B>It was in this time, that a Queen among them made it her quest to bring these tribes together.  With other's of the Nation, they met and bonded in strength and unity.  In an attempt to put away pride of themselves and turn it into pride of a nation, they formed the Amazon Nation Alliance.</B></I></P><br>
<br>
<br>
<P ALIGN=Center><br>
<I><B>Now, as the outlying Empires move to close in on these Amazons who threaten their male egos...these women stand together.  United.   </B></I></P><br>
<br>
<H1 ALIGN=Center><I><B>Amazons Unite!</B></I></H1><br>
